        ]
      },
      "level": {
        "value": 2
      },
      "privateNotes": "",
      "publicNotes": "<p><strong>Role:</strong> a deserter-guard thug (one of Verik's four 'Cow Hammer Boys'), reusable as a Northgate brigand. Opens with the longbow, closes to the club only if forced.</p><p><strong>Tactics &amp; morale:</strong> two guard the front (B1), two work the killing floor (B4). A boy at low HP flees into the city; once two are dead, the rest abandon Verik and run. They do <strong>not</strong> let anyone up to Verik — they hide their murder-for-hire side business from him.</p>",
      "publication": {
        "title": "Pathfinder: Curse of the Crimson Throne (PF2e conversion, private)",
        "authors": "",
        "license": "OGL",
        "remaster": true
      }
